snippet.title: Acossi Brand
snippet.description:
Acossi Group Holding was Acossi music / Records but is now the umbrella company 
That carries its own fashion brand and offers services for design and sale Consumer products related to our trademark Acossi

Our brand

Acossi jeans
Contemporary casual Fashion brand
www.acossijeans.com

Design Services
www.lcreativeconcept.acossi.com

We still holds rights to all our music releases and distribute online music. 

By Natacha Lacosse
